OL,7,FComedian Rhod Gilbert has received a
OL,8,Fclear scan for the first time since
OL,9,Fbeing diagnosed with cancer.
OL,11,FThe 55-year-old Welshman announced in
OL,12,FJuly 2022 that he had the disease and
OL,13,Fwas being treated at the Velindre
OL,14,FCancer Centre in Cardiff, where he
OL,15,Fhad been a fundraising patron for a
OL,16,Fdecade before the diagnosis.
OL,18,FHe underwent surgery for metastatic
OL,19,Fcancer of the head and neck, followed
OL,20,Fby sessions of chemotherapy and
OL,21,Fradiotherapy.
OL,3,CRhod Gilbert says first clear scan
OL,4,Cafter cancer diagnosis was 'the best
OL,5,Cday of my life'
